{"type":"message","id":"41831b5e","parentId":"3e0d8782","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:31:21.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me spawn the first 4 agents in parallel for Phase 1 tasks. I'll create sessions for them.","thinkingSignature":"7450457884c0fb3d3af1adf6917a4da760942156be79ad37b04477c4b6a2fd99"},{"type":"text","text":"Giờ spawn 4 agents Phase 1 song song:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xxh0gzsii5z2_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are senior-architect. Design the system architecture for the AHV Tech Knowledge Hub project.\n\nProject location: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/\n\nRead the OpenSpec first: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/proposal.md\n\nYour task (T1): Design system architecture.\n\nDeliverables — write to /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/architecture.md:\n\n1. **App Structure**: Next.js 14 App Router folder layout with rationale\n2. **Data Flow**: How content (MDX articles) flows from file → API → UI\n3. **Component Architecture**: How components are organized (shared, feature-based)\n4. **Real-time Architecture**: Socket.IO integration with Next.js (api routes vs custom server)\n5. **Music Integration**: YouTube/Spotify embed strategy\n6. **SEO Architecture**: How next-seo + JSON-LD integrates with App Router\n7. **Database Schema Preview**: High-level MongoDB collections needed\n8. **Deployment Strategy**: Vercel setup, env vars, ISR revalidation\n\nTech stack to use:\n- Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui\n- Framer Motion for animations\n- MDX for content, next-mdx-remote or @next/mdx\n- Socket.IO for real-time\n- MongoDB (Mongoose)\n- next-seo, next-sitemap\n\nAfter writing the file, reply with a brief summary of what you designed.","label":"ahv-knowledge-hub:senior-architect","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"senior-architect","mode":"run"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xxh0gzsii5z2_2","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are content-strategy. Define the content strategy for the AHV Tech Knowledge Hub.\n\nProject location: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/\n\nRead the OpenSpec first: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/proposal.md\n\nYour task (T5): Define content pillars, topic clusters, and content plan.\n\nDeliverables — write to /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/content-strategy.md:\n\n1. **Content Pillars** (3-4 pillars, each with mission statement):\n   - CTDL & Giải thuật: Các thuật toán, cấu trúc dữ liệu cơ bản → nâng cao\n   - AI & Machine Learning: Từ beginner-friendly → advanced\n   - Web Dev & DevOps: Thực hành, hướng dẫn step-by-step\n   - CS Fundamentals: OS, Networks, DB, v.v.\n\n2. **Topic Clusters** per pillar (5-8 topics each with search intent)\n\n3. **Content Formats**:\n   - Tutorial (how-to, step-by-step)\n   - Explainers (concept deep-dives)\n   - Comparisons (X vs Y)\n   - Cheat sheets\n   - Code walkthroughs\n\n4. **Editorial Calendar Suggestion**: 2-3 articles/week cadence\n5. **SEO Keywords**: Primary + secondary keywords per pillar (Vietnamese + English mix)\n6. **Content Quality Standards**: What makes a \"chuẩn chỉnh\" article (structure, depth, code quality)\n7. **Content Examples**: 5 article titles per pillar for initial seeding\n\nWrite the file now. Reply briefly when done.","label":"ahv-knowledge-hub:content-strategy","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"content-strategy","mode":"run"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xxh0gzsii5z2_3","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are ai-seo. Create a comprehensive SEO strategy for the AHV Tech Knowledge Hub.\n\nProject location: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/\n\nRead the OpenSpec first: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/proposal.md\n\nYour task (T6): SEO strategy and structured data schema.\n\nDeliverables — write to /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/seo-strategy.md:\n\n1. **Keyword Strategy**:\n   - Seed keywords per content pillar (CTDL, AI, Web Dev, DevOps, CS)\n   - Long-tail opportunities for Vietnamese tech audience\n   - Competitor keywords to outrank\n\n2. **Technical SEO Checklist**:\n   - Sitemap.xml strategy (static vs dynamic routes)\n   - Robots.txt\n   - Canonical URLs\n   - hreflang (if multi-language future)\n   - Core Web Vitals targets (LCP < 2.5s, CLS < 0.1, FID < 100ms)\n   - Image optimization (WebP, lazy load, blur placeholders)\n   - Font optimization\n\n3. **On-Page SEO**:\n   - Meta title template: \"{article_title} | AHV Tech Hub\"\n   - Meta description template\n   - Open Graph template for articles\n   - Twitter card setup\n   - Heading hierarchy (H1 per page, H2-H3 for sections)\n   - Internal linking strategy\n\n4. **JSON-LD Structured Data Schemas**:\n   - Article schema (full code example)\n   - BreadcrumbList schema\n   - FAQPage schema (for how-to articles)\n   - WebSite schema with SearchAction\n   - Person schema (author)\n\n5. **Content SEO**:\n   - Readability: Flesch-Kincaid target for Vietnamese audience\n   - Code snippet SEO (syntax highlighting, descriptive alt text)\n   - Image alt text guidelines\n   - Internal linking anchor text rules\n\n6. **Off-Page SEO**:\n   - Backlink strategy\n   - Social share optimization\n\nWrite the file now. Reply briefly when done.","label":"ahv-knowledge-hub:ai-seo","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"ai-seo","mode":"run"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xxh0gzsii5z2_4","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are ui-ux-pro-max. Create wireframes for the AHV Tech Knowledge Hub.\n\nProject location: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/\n\nRead the OpenSpec first: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/proposal.md\n\nYour task (T3): Create wireframes for all 5 core pages.\n\nWrite wireframes as detailed text-based layout descriptions + component breakdowns to:\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/wireframes.md\n\nPages to wireframe:\n\n1. **Home Page**:\n   - Hero: tagline + CTA (khám phá ngay)\n   - Featured article (large card)\n   - Category strip (CTDL, AI, Web Dev, CS, DevOps)\n   - Recent posts grid (3-col desktop, 1-col mobile)\n   - Music preview widget (mini player)\n   - Newsletter signup\n   - Footer\n\n2. **Article Detail Page**:\n   - Header: title, author, date, reading time, tags\n   - TOC sidebar (sticky, desktop)\n   - Article body (MDX rendered)\n   - Code blocks with copy button\n   - Author bio card\n   - Related posts (3 cards)\n   - Share buttons\n   - Comment section placeholder\n\n3. **Music Page (Relaxation Zone)**:\n   - Mood selector (Focus, Sleep, Energize, Study)\n   - Active playlist with album art\n   - Persistent mini-player bar\n   - Queue / history\n   - Lyrics sidebar (if available)\n\n4. **Live Study Room Page**:\n   - Room code input + join button\n   - Pomodoro timer (large, centered)\n   - Participant list (avatars + names)\n   - Current session goal\n   - Break notification\n   - Ambient background (optional)\n\n5. **Search Results Page**:\n   - Search bar (large, prominent)\n   - Filter pills (category, tag, date)\n   - Results list with snippet preview\n   - Pagination\n   - Empty state design\n\nFor each page include:\n- Mobile layout (375px) description\n- Tablet layout (768px) description\n- Desktop layout (1280px) description\n- Component inventory (button states, card variants, etc.)\n- Dark/Light mode color direction\n\nWrite the file now. Reply briefly when done.","label":"ahv-knowledge-hub:ui-ux-pro-max","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"ui-ux-pro-max","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":113,"output":2099,"cacheRead":31231,"cacheWrite":2812,"totalTokens":36255,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776569445620,"responseId":"06337f66cc529ab2d2b3f823f1273a0a"}}
