{"type":"message","id":"902a5a07","parentId":"0292cd0e","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:32:29.283Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ygbxjhj8dief_1","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:product-marketing-context:subagent:72ceb1f5-26ed-473a-a6c0-68f9d1158a5d\",\n  \"runId\": \"263eaaab-cd81-4ed5-9f5f-1d9c3511999a\",\n  \"mode\": \"run\",\n  \"note\": \"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.\",\n  \"modelApplied\": true\n}"}],"details":{"status":"accepted","childSessionKey":"agent:product-marketing-context:subagent:72ceb1f5-26ed-473a-a6c0-68f9d1158a5d","runId":"263eaaab-cd81-4ed5-9f5f-1d9c3511999a","mode":"run","note":"Auto-announce is push-based. After spawning children, do NOT call sessions_list, sessions_history, exec sleep, or any polling tool. Wait for completion events to arrive as user messages, track expected child session keys, and only send your final answer after ALL expected completions arrive. If a child completion event arrives AFTER your final answer, reply ONLY with NO_REPLY.","modelApplied":true},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776569549231}}
{"type":"message","id":"87efde70","parentId":"902a5a07","timestamp":"2026-04-19T03:32:35.634Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. 5 agents spawned. Now let me report to the Lead on what's been set up and what's running.","thinkingSignature":"0db74cb784723bdddfb68c3428c70ad9adbcbe59d1c5e3b35924c3b2547412ab"},{"type":"text","text":"\n✅ **OpenSpec đã tạo xong.** Đang chạy Phase 1 song song:\n\n| Agent | Task | Status |\n|---|---|---|\n| senior-architect | System architecture (Next.js, Socket.IO, SEO) | 🚀 Running |\n| content-strategy | Content pillars CTDL/AI/CS + editorial calendar | 🚀 Running |\n| ai-seo | Keywords, JSON-LD schemas, technical SEO | 🚀 Running |\n| ui-ux-pro-max | Wireframes cho 5 core pages | 🚀 Running |\n| product-marketing-context | Brand voice, ICP, competitive positioning | 🚀 Running |\n\n**Khi nào 4 agents trên xong → senior-frontend sẽ scaffold Next.js project và bắt đầu build.**\n\nTrong lúc chờ, Lead muốn mình đặt tên chính thức cho dự án chưa? Hiện tạm gọi là \"AHV Tech Knowledge Hub\" — có đổi gì không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":254,"output":249,"cacheRead":36892,"cacheWrite":1332,"totalTokens":38727,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776569549285,"responseId":"06337fce98f363753da9b94dc6198735"}}
