{"type":"message","id":"f09fcd8e","parentId":"275392fc","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:19:14.968Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jv3cbennvi5e_1","toolName":"gitlab__gitlab_create_merge_request","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": 475358762,\n  \"iid\": 1,\n  \"project_id\": 81439240,\n  \"title\": \"feat(maiy): scaffold MAIY Tech Hub — Phase 1 + Phase 2\",\n  \"description\": \"## MAIY Tech Hub — Initial Scaffold\\n\\n### What\\n- Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript + Tailwind + shadcn/ui\\n- Pages: Home, Articles listing, Article detail, Music, Study, Search\\n- SEO: sitemap, robots, JSON-LD Article schema, breadcrumbs\\n- Design: Dark/light mode, responsive, smooth UI\\n- Music: Mood selector (Focus/Sleep/Energize/Study), YouTube embeds, persistent mini-player\\n- Study: Pomodoro timer (25/5), room create/join, participant list, ambient sounds\\n- shadcn/ui: button, card, badge, input, dialog, sheet, avatar, separator\\n- Socket.IO: server.ts with room events + pomodoro sync\\n- Hooks: use-socket.ts, use-pomodoro.ts\\n\\n### Content\\n8 MDX articles across 5 categories:\\n- CTDL: Binary Search, Dynamic Programming\\n- AI: Linear Regression Python, Neural Network from scratch\\n- Web Dev: Next.js App Router, Docker Compose\\n- CS Fundamentals: Stack & Heap Memory\\n- DevOps: GitHub Actions CI/CD\\n\\n### Build Status\\n- `yarn build` ✅ (12/12 static pages)\\n- `yarn lint` ✅ (no warnings)\\n\\n### Tech Stack\\nNext.js 14, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Framer Motion, Socket.IO, MDX\\n\\n---\\n@khuowgn please review and merge.\",\n  \"state\": \"opened\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-04-19T04:19:14.657Z\",\n  \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-19T04:19:14.657Z\",\n  \"merged_by\": null,\n  \"merge_user\": null,\n  \"merged_at\": null,\n  \"closed_by\": null,\n  \"closed_at\": null,\n  \"target_branch\": \"develop\",\n  \"source_branch\": \"feat/scaffold-initial\",\n  \"user_notes_count\": 0,\n  \"upvotes\": 0,\n  \"downvotes\": 0,\n  \"au