{"type":"message","id":"d78868a8","parentId":"00c187e5","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:34:32.504Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear list of all emoji usage. Let me replace them with Lucide icons. I'll rewrite the affected files.Lucide icons available:\n- 💡 → Lightbulb\n- 🚀 → Rocket\n- 📚 → BookOpen\n- 🎵 → Music / Headphones\n- 🎯 → Target / Crosshair\n- ⚡ → Zap\n- 😴 → Moon\n- 🌧️ → CloudRain\n- ☕ → Coffee\n- 📖 → Book\n- 🔍 → Search\n- ✅ → CheckCircle\n\n\n- ❌ → XCircle\n- ⏱️ → Timer\n- 🍅 → (no tomato in Lucide) → Clock\n- ❤️ → Heart\n- 📌 → Pin\n- 💬 → MessageCircle\n- 🎉 → PartyPopper\n- ⏳ → Hourglass\n- ⏰ → AlarmClock\n- 📝 → FileText\n- 📋 → ClipboardList\n- 🔥 → Flame\n- ✨ → Sparkles\n- 🎓 → GraduationCap\n- 💻 → Laptop\n- 🌙 → Moon\n- 🔗 → Link\n\nContinuing with more Lucide icon replacements...","thinkingSignature":"73f7d941f9deaf64f4dfaba2dda951d389a80e1b60a1155b610780e0c3c33f07"},{"type":"text","text":"Rõ ràng. Giờ replace toàn bộ emoji bằng Lucide icons:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q3em4trykp0r_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/layout/header.tsx","content":"'use client'\n\nimport Link from 'next/link'\nimport { usePathname } from 'next/navigation'\nimport { useTheme } from 'next-themes'\nimport { useState, useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { Search, Moon, Sun, Menu, X, Lightbulb } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { cn } from '@/lib/utils'\nimport { ThemeToggle } from '@/components/shared/theme-toggle'\n\nconst NAV_LINKS = [\n  { href: '/articles', label: 'Bài viết' },\n  { href: '/music', label: 'Âm nhạc' },\n  { href: '/study', label: 'Học live' },\n  { href: '/about', label: 'Giới thiệu' },\n]\n\nexport function Header() {\n  const pathname = usePathname()\n  const { theme } = useTheme()\n  const [mounted, setMounted] = useState(false)\n  const [mobileOpen, setMobileOpen] = useState(false)\n\n  useEffect(() => setMounted(true), [])\n\n  return (\n    <header className=\"sticky top-0 z-50 w-full border-b border-border/40 bg-background/95 backdrop-blur supports-[backdrop-filter]:bg-background/60\">\n      <div className=\"container flex h-16 items-center justify-between\">\n        {/* Logo */}\n        <Link href=\"/\" className=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-xl\">\n          <Lightbulb className=\"h-6 w-6 text-indigo-500\" />\n          <span className=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">\n            MAIY Tech Hub\n          </span>\n        </Link>\n\n        {/* Desktop Nav */}\n        <nav className=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6\">\n          {NAV_LINKS.map((link) => (\n            <Link\n              key={link.href}\n              href={link.href}\n              className={cn(\n                'text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:text-primary',\n                pathname?.startsWith(link.href)\n                  ? 'text-primary'\n                  : 'text-muted-foreground'\n              )}\n            >\n              {link.label}\n            </Link>\n          ))}\n        </nav>\n\n        {/* Right side */}\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          <Link\n            href=\"/search\"\n            className=\"p-2 rounded-md hover:bg-accent transition-colors\"\n            aria-label=\"Tìm kiếm\"\n          >\n            <Search className=\"h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground\" />\n          </Link>\n\n          {mounted && <ThemeToggle />}\n\n          {/* Mobile menu button */}\n          <button\n            className=\"md:hidden p-2 rounded-md hover:bg-accent transition-colors\"\n            onClick={() => setMobileOpen(!mobileOpen)}\n            aria-label=\"Menu\"\n          >\n            {mobileOpen ? (\n              <X className=\"h-5 w-5\" />\n            ) : (\n              <Menu className=\"h-5 w-5\" />\n            )}\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Mobile Nav */}\n      {mobileOpen && (\n        <div className=\"md:hidden border-t border-border/40 bg-background\">\n          <nav className=\"container py-4 flex flex-col gap-2\">\n            {NAV_LINKS.map((link) => (\n              <Link\n                key={link.href}\n                href={link.href}\n                onClick={() => setMobileOpen(false)}\n                className={cn(\n                  'px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-accent',\n                  pathname?.startsWith(link.href)\n                    ? 'bg-accent text-primary'\n                    : 'text-muted-foreground'\n                )}\n              >\n                {link.label}\n              </Link>\n            ))}\n          </nav>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </header>\n  )\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q3em4trykp0r_2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/layout/footer.tsx","content":"import Link from 'next/link'\nimport { Lightbulb, Github, Heart } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { CATEGORIES } from '@/config/site'\n\nexport function Footer() {\n  const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear()\n\n  return (\n    <footer className=\"border-t border-border/40 bg-muted/30\">\n      <div className=\"container py-12\">\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\">\n          {/* Brand */}\n          <div className=\"md:col-span-2\">\n            <Link href=\"/\" className=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-lg mb-3\">\n              <Lightbulb className=\"h-5 w-5 text-indigo-500\" />\n              <span>MAIY Tech Hub</span>\n            </Link>\n            <p className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-sm\">\n              Nền tảng blog chia sẻ kiến thức CNTT chuẩn chỉnh bằng tiếng Việt.\n              Code thật, giải thích dễ hiểu.\n            </p>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-4\">\n              <a\n                href=\"https://github.com/khuowgn/maiy-tech-hub\"\n                target=\"_blank\"\n                rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n                className=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors\"\n                aria-label=\"GitHub\"\n              >\n                <Github className=\"h-5 w-5\" />\n              </a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Categories */}\n          <div>\n            <h3 className=\"font-semibold mb-4 text-sm\">Chủ đề</h3>\n            <ul className=\"space-y-2\">\n              {CATEGORIES.map((cat) => (\n                <li key={cat.slug}>\n                  <Link\n                    href={`/articles/category/${cat.slug}`}\n                    className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors\"\n                  >\n                    {cat.label}\n                  </Link>\n                </li>\n              ))}\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Links */}\n          <div>\n            <h3 className=\"font-semibold mb-4 text-sm\">Liên kết</h3>\n            <ul className=\"space-y-2\">\n              {[\n                { href: '/about', label: 'Giới thiệu' },\n                { href: '/articles', label: 'Tất cả bài viết' },\n                { href: '/music', label: 'Âm nhạc' },\n                { href: '/study', label: 'Phòng học live' },\n                { href: '/search', label: 'Tìm kiếm' },\n              ].map((link) => (\n                <li key={link.href}>\n                  <Link\n                    href={link.href}\n                    className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors\"\n                  >\n                    {link.label}\n                  </Link>\n                </li>\n              ))}\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-border/40 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4\">\n          <p className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\n            © {currentYear} MAIY Tech Hub. Kiến thức vì cộng đồng.\n          </p>\n          <p className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-1\">\n            Built with Next.js\n            <Heart className=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500 inline\" />\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </footer>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":787,"output":2056,"cacheRead":142583,"cacheWrite":647,"totalTokens":146073,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776573247336,"responseId":"06338e41bf1537d12dfcc13bc3f12ab4"}}
